  <h2 class="section-title-small text-center">Commodity Background</h2>
        <section class="com-additional-wrapper com-chart-wrapper clearfix">
      <div class="container text-center">

        
                            <div class="com-desc col-xs-12 col-sm-12">
            <div class="chart-desc text-left"><p>
                </p><p class="rtecenter">About three-quarters of all U.S. grain products, such as bread, pasta, and cookies, are made from wheat flour. Outside of the U.S., wheat is also regularly used for animal feed. In the European Union, almost half of wheat production is used to feed animals. &nbsp;</p>
              <p></p>
            </div>
          </div>
              </div>
    </section>
  
